title: Tek Republic TUH-200 USB 3.0 +2.0 4 Port Hub
description: OverviewThe The Tek Republic USB 3.0 + 2.0 4 Port Hub (TUH-200) allows you to transfer data at blazing speeds of up to 5 Gbps (up to 10 times faster than USB 2.0) through one USB 3.0 Port. It's fully compatible between USB 3.0/2.0/1.1 hosts and devices. With three USB 2.0 Ports it allows you to connect other USB Peripherals - such as printers, mice, keyboards, webcams, etc. With a slim and compact design it makes it easy to fit in a laptop bag and carry it with you, wherever you go. Experience the convenience and reliability with Tek Republic USB 3.0 + 2.0 4 Port Hub while on the go.DesignCompact, sleek and light weight designPerformance1 Port USB 3.0 and 3 Port USB 2.0. Providing data rates of up to 5Gbps - 10 times faster than USB 2.0.PowerBus powered.CompatibilityCompatible with Windows XP, Vista, 7, 8, Mac OS X, and Linux. Fully backward compatibility with USB 1.1 hosts and devices.What's in the BoxTUH-200 1 Port USB 3.0 & 3 Port USB 2.0 4-Port HubSpecificationsDimensions: 3.8 x 0.9 x 0.7 inchesWeight: 4oz
